{"word":"G3666 - ὁμοιόω - homoióō - hom-oy-o'-o - Be like","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁμοιόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">homoióō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hom-oy-o'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be like</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஒப்பிடு, ஒத்திரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to make like"},{"paragraph":"2. to liken, compare"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3664 - ὅμοιος - hómoios - hom'-oy-os/3664\">G3664</a>; to <i>assimilate</i>, that is, <i>compare</i>; passively to <i>become similar:</i> - be (make) like, (in the) liken (-ess), resemble.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3664/3664\">G3664</a>, <a href=\"#/G3665/3665\">G3665</a>, <a href=\"#/G3666/3666\">G3666</a>, <a href=\"#/G3667/3667\">G3667</a>, <a href=\"#/G3668/3668\">G3668</a>, <a href=\"#/G3669/3669\">G3669</a>, <a href=\"#/G3670/3670\">G3670</a>, <a href=\"#/G3945/3945\">G3945</a>, <a href=\"#/G3946/3946\">G3946</a>, <a href=\"#/G871/871\">G871</a>"}]}